#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:1046
msgid ":kbd:`Shift`: add features to the current selection"
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift`: aggiunge geometrie alla selezione corrente"

#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:1047
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl`: substract features from the current selection"
