msgid ""
"Beside many options in the vector layer properties dialog or settings in the"
" print composer, you can find a |dataDefined| :sup:`Data defined override` "
"icon. Thanks to :ref:`expressions <vector_expressions>` based on layer "
"attributes or item settings, prebuild or custom functions and "
